      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. It has been meticulously maintained by a single owner, with a flawless exterior finish and a pristine interior that still smells new. Every mechanical component functions perfectly, and the service history is comprehensive and up-to-date. This is a rare find for a buyer seeking a used car in truly perfect, investment-grade condition.",
